social_posts.post_text: Oh. So AI is just out here fully convincing people to get married now, huh? Fine. I’ll do a domestic partnership if I can wear this.

It’s no secret that the wig department at @bttfbway are a group of superstars. So they deserve to be compensated like the stars that they are. A show as big as this one would not be able to run without them. The Broadway hairstylists and makeup artists of IATSE LOCAL 798 deserve fair contracts and live-able wages. They have not been able to re-negotiate their contracts for years and it is long overdue. We have to fight for our friends. They need your help. They need pay equity. They need fair contracts.

@newyorkdress, thank you so so much for everything. @jontaylorphoto, you are a dream. @bttfbway, I can’t believe we are just getting started.

I’ve had the blessing of opening up 3 Broadway shows since our industry returned after the pandemic. I still think of the days I was sat in my parents basement. Waiting for the day to do the thing that I love again. The thing I truly feel is my purpose. Last night was not lost on me. I’m so grateful to work on Broadway. I’m so grateful to open another show.. and I’m so grateful my mom and dad got to see me do it. @rebeccajmichelson @newyorkdress @no.standing.nyc @samgen_makeup @bttfbway
Beyoncé. Baby showers. Back to the Future… and football? Weird week.
Happy Opening Night of @bttfbway from The McFly’s. It’s a gift to be in a show where every night feels like an opening night.

Cannot believe that it’s time to say I have 1 month left with the beautiful company of @bttfbway. My final performance as Linda McFly will be on December 30th. This show is everything that I needed to fuel my love of performing. I love this show. I love the people who created it, and I will be the most sad to part ways with it. I hope I get to see you all at The Wintergarden before my final date. Love, Linda McFly 🤍

Introducing Back to the Futures new Linda McFly! My God, Katie. It’s your TIME. Getting to watch you make your Broadway debut from this perspective is everything I could have ever wanted. There isn’t a better feeling than having your best friend of 10+ years accomplish one of her dreams…and now I get to be along for the ride of it with you. I LOVE YOU LINDA! 🤍🍾🎉 #bestfriendsonBROADWAY #LindaMcDouble #broadwayfookingdebut
